w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/hiroyuki-sanada@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/hiroyuki-sanada@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/shogun"><em>幕府</em></a>将军真田广之正在洽谈出演即将上映的真人电影《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/ghost-of-tsushima"><em>对马岛之魂》</em></a> 。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/shogun-finale-season-2-what-now-3749403">生死大结局之后，“幕府将军”现在怎么办？</a></strong></li></ul><p>据可靠的电影业内人士<a href="https://www.patreon.com/posts/105254279?utm_campaign=postshare_creator&amp;utm_source=android" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>DanielRPK</em></a>报道，据<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/shogun-star-in-talks-for-ghost-of-tsushima-film-role" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Eurogamer</em></a>报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony-pictures">索尼影业</a>和 PlayStation Productions 正在寻求让真田在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/ghost-of-tsushima-film-script-finished-amid-strikes-you-have-to-will-things-into-existence-3527960">电影<em>《对马岛之魂》</em></a>中扮演一个未公开的角色。真田的选角尚未确定。</p><p>真田在<em>《对马岛之魂》</em>中的潜在角色不会超出这位受人尊敬的日本演员过去的作品。除了<em>《幕府将军》</em>之外，真田还主演了多部武士电影（日文和英文），例如<em>《最后的武士》</em> 、 <em>《47罗尼</em>》、《<em>八武士传说》</em> 、《幕府将军<em>的忍者》</em> 、 <em>《武士转世</em>》、 <em>《幕府将军的武士</em>》、 <em>《暮光武士》</em>和更多。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594564" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594564" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594564" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024.jpg" alt="&#39;将军&#39;" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/shogun_disney_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594564" class="wp-caption-text">真田广之饰演虎长吉井。图片来源：Kurt Iswarienko/FX</figcaption></figure><p>他还主演了视频游戏改编的电影，最著名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/mortal-kombat-review-2926848">2021 年重启的<em>《真人快打》</em></a>和明年的<em>《真人快打》</em>续集。他主演的其他电影和电视剧包括<em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em> 、 <em>《鹰眼》</em> 、 <em>《疾速追杀：第四章》</em> 、 <em>《迷失》</em>和<em>《西部世界》</em> 。</p><p> 《对<em>马岛之魂》</em>电影的演员阵容尚未公布。该片将由查德·斯塔赫斯基执导，他因<em>《疾速追杀》</em>系列而闻名。索尼影业和 PlayStation Productions <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-live-action-ghost-of-tsushima-film-is-in-the-works-2909888">于 2021 年宣布改编</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sucker-punch">Sucker Punch Productions</a>担任执行制片人。目前尚不清楚《对<em>马岛之魂》</em>的剧本是日语还是英语，因为游戏的对话最初是用日语提供的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3120122" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3120122" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3120122" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut.jpg" alt="对马岛之魂" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Ghost-of-Tsushima-Directors-Cut-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3120122" class="wp-caption-text">对马岛的幽灵。信用：Sucker Punch</figcaption></figure><p>乔丹·奥洛曼 (Jordan Oloman) 在<em>《NME》</em>对<em>《对马岛之魂》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/ghost-of-tsushima-review-a-serene-samurai-simulator-paired-with-a-lacklustre-storyline-2707317">四星评论</a>中写道：“如果你还没有看出来， <em>《对马岛之魂》</em>是一部鱼龙混杂的作品。从技术角度来看，它在任何方面都没有失败——它演奏得很好，听起来很棒，看起来也令人难以置信，但更精细的音符降低了它的整体阻止能力。只要您能接受一些奇怪的设计选择，就物有所值而言，很容易推荐。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/shogun-star-hiroyuki-sanada-is-reportedly-in-talks-for-ghost-of-tsushima-film-3764358">据报道，《幕府将军》后的主演真田博之正在洽谈拍摄《对马岛之魂》的电影，该电影</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
